    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Roll'N With Da Punchez&quot; is a stylized, physics-based platformer where you don’t just guide a ball… You Punch It! Launch a punch-propelled ball through vibrant abstract obstacle courses and reach the goal with precise strikes. But stay alert, one bad move could send the ball back to the ground! But don't let that get you down! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is all about making mistakes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269380/extras/829a5a8adf34bd2d8711f25d15da7bdd.poster.avif?t=1767978768\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269380/extras/829a5a8adf34bd2d8711f25d15da7bdd.webm?t=1767978768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269380/extras/829a5a8adf34bd2d8711f25d15da7bdd.mp4?t=1767978768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So have fun:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traversing through challenging obstacle courses with unique puzzles and hazards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solving those same puzzles by punching everything with a charge-based system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Punching colorful balls with unique powers to spice up your experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trying Optional Challenges to test your skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suffering</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
